source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_SEQ_00<tab>Ponnixia just wants to take her mind off her troubles.
target: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_SEQ_00<tab>Ponnixia a envie d'un petit remontant.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_SEQ_01<tab>Ponnixia is finding fun to be elusive in recent days, and seeks to acquire dreamslime to enhance the potency of her beloved milkroot. Unfortunately, the much sought-after substance is being monopolized by selfish touched ones. Acquire four phials of dreamtoad ooze, either straight from the source or from the inebriated sylphs who are already partaking in its pleasures.
target: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_SEQ_01<tab>Ponnixia a envie de tuberculait, et pas n'importe lequel<var 1D /var>: il lui faut une pointe de mucus de crapaud rêveur dedans. Vous devez donc lui rapporter quatre <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E88E10302 /var>, que vous pourrez obtenir en tuant des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DA50302 /var> ou des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0D450302 /var> dans les Terres sylphes.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_SEQ_02<tab>You have obtained four phials of the unsightly yet highly treasured ooze. Deliver the goods to Ponnixia.
target: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez suf<var 16 /var>fi<var 16 /var>sam<var 16 /var>ment de mucus de crapaud rêveur. Retournez les porter à Ponnixia au Refuge.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_SEQ_03<tab>Ponnixia's eyes light up at the sight of the ooze. While the potent milkroot concoction will not resolve the many troubles that her people face, it will at least serve to return smiles to their faces.
target: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_SEQ_03<tab>Ponnixia va pouvoir s'offrir un bon petit remontant, et même plusieurs, grâce à vous. Nul doute qu'il vous en est très re<var 16 /var>con<var 16 /var>nais<var 16 /var>sant.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_TODO_00<tab>Defeat dreamtoads or sylpheed sighs to obtain phials of dreamtoad ooze.
target: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_TODO_00<tab>Obtenir 4 fioles de mucus de crapaud rêveur en tuant des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DA50302 /var> ou des <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0D450302 /var> dans les Terres sylphes

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the phials of dreamtoad ooze to Ponnixia.
target: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_TODO_01<tab>Apporter les fioles à Ponnixia au Refuge

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_000<tab>Does walking one know what these ones love even more than milkroot? Milkroot mixed with dreamslime! Dreamslime makes milkroot thrice as fun, tee hee!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_000Tu sais ce qui me ferait du bien?
D'un peu de tuberculait dans l'heure!
Et avec une pointe de mucus de crapaud rêveur,
le goût en devient di-vin!

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_001<tab>But this one isn't having much fun today. Why? Because touched ones are herding slimy ones and hoarding all the dreamslime!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_001Je préfère en avoir toujours de côté,
Il n'y a, crois-moi, rien de pire qu'en manquer.
Quatre racines, oui, ça devrait suffire,
des , tu peux les obtenir.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_002<tab>Walking one must punish touched ones and steal dreamslime─teach touched ones not to be greedy ones!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_002Les en ont eux aussi,
ils se gardent les crapauds et se servent sans merci.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_003<tab>...Or just find slimy one and bring dreamslime to this one, so this one can forget one's worries.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_003Ces animaux ne sont à personne,
mais les Dénaturés égoïstement les braconnent!

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_005<tab>Touched ones are herding slimy ones and hoarding all the dreamslime! Walking one must teach touched ones not to be greedy ones. Or just find slimy one and bring dreamslime to this one, so this one can forget one's worries.
target:
TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_005Quatre fioles de mucus, oui, ça devrait suffire,
des , tu peux les obtenir.
Les en ont eux aussi,
ils gardent les crapauds et se servent sans merci.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_010<tab>This one is having no fun, no fun at all! Did friendly one find dreamslime for this one?
target:
TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_010Quatre fioles de mucus, oui, ça devrait suffire,
des , tu peux les obtenir.
Les en ont eux aussi,
ils gardent les crapauds et se servent sans merci.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_012<tab>Friendly one brings dreamslime! At long last, this one can be smiling one again!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_012Cette bonne odeur de mucus me ravit l'appendice,
c'est une promesse enjôleuse de futurs délices.

source: TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_013<tab>These ones have many worries these days. Without milkroot and dreamslime, these ones would be frowning and brooding ones, and what would be the fun in that? Tee hee!
target:
TEXT_BANSYL202_01268_PONNIXIA_000_013Tu as toute ma gratitude,
Ô d'une telle béatitude!
